description:
This Fingerprint Lock Screen cannot really identify your fingerprint, it's just a simulated app used for fun.
Fingerprint Lock Screen Prank is a pretty customizable screen locker that simulates the finger scan to unlock your phone screen. When

you press your finger on the fingerprint detector panel, the fingerprint scanner will start to scan your fingerprint and verify the

authority. The phone will be unlocked if the validation passes, otherwise the phone screen will still be locked.

Finger Print Lock Screen provides several cool hi-tech wallpapers for you to customize your phone screen. In order to be your better

phone lock screensaver, this fingerprint locker shows you current weather, weather forecast, clock and date right on screen as well.



How To Use FingerPrint Lock Screen :
-----------------------------------------------------------

1.Place your finger on the thumb scanner panel and scan your finger print, It starts giving you a beep.
2.Remove your finger from the fingerprint sensor when 2 Sound`s (2 times BEEP) completes, It will Unlock your phone.
3.Your Device will still be locked if it gives you more than 2 Sound`s (BEEP) or less than 2 Sound`s ( BEEP ).
4.You can change Number of sounds (Beep) to unlock your device from Settings.
5.By default sound is set to 2 times announcement. you can set Number of sounds to unlock your phone as per you need. If you change

the Number of sound = 4 , it means that you will have to scan your thumb till 4 times sound announces to unlock.

Features Of Fingerprint Lock Screen Prank:
------------------------------------------
1.High-tech graphic and sounds which make you phone look like a high-tech Hologram device.
2.Shows digital clock, date and time.
3.Provide clear guide and easy to used.
4.Disable the home button, no one can unlock the phone with the home button.
5.More than 15 brilliant and beautiful wallpapers are provided.

Note that this app is intended to simulate a fingerprint reader and Android phone does not have this feature yet. Obviously the phone screen can not be used as a biometric fingerprint scanner for now. This technology is to be supported from hardware.
This is not a secure replacement for a real lock screen and is not for reasons of simulator. fingerprint screen lock is designed for entertainment purposes only.


Disclaimer:
-----------------
The fingerprint scan is a simulated feature, it is just for fun.This Fingerprint lock screen prank is designed for fun & entertainment purposes only

description:
貴方が持っている資質、性格、運気力を知る宿命と、毎日の運勢を示す後天運を占います。

　宝田村の占星術は、生年月日により、自分の持っている宿命と人生の運勢を示す後天運を四柱推命を利用して占います。

　自然の中ですべてのものがこの理の中で営まれていると考え、その自然により与えられた理を知り、それに寄り添い、自己練磨を経験することにより喜びが得られると考えます。

　どう一生を過ごしていくか。それは貴方に与えられた、時間、性格、人間力、出会った人で決まっていきます。
　自分の性格を知ることにより、向いている仕事があり、人間関係、恋愛関係も無理をせずに心休まる関係を選択できます。

　自分のバイオリズムを知ることにより、気持ちの浮き沈みがあることも納得することができます。
　長い道のり、落ち着いた時を過ごすためにも、自分を知ることは大切なことです。

『宿命が解ります』
　貴方が持っている資質、性格、運気力です。人格、人生の選択、社会的運勢を司ります。生年月日、そこから貴方の宿命は決まります。

『主星』
　あなたの主星は、あなたにとって一番良い働きをする星です。これからの人生に最も影響します。
　その主星に逆らわず、また活かしていくことが幸せの始まりでもあります。

『従星』
　従星は、運気力（運気の大きさ）を持った星です。
　

『１０年運』の運勢
　人生は１０年間を区切りとして、支配する主星と従星が変わります。
　巡る主星は人それぞれ違います。また巡る順番もそれぞれ異なります。
　自分に巡ってきた主星の空間を生かすことが大切です。
　１０年運は、主星より従星のほうが運勢に大きな影響を与えます。
　大きなエネルギーを持っているときは大きな影響があります。
　その支配している主星と従星が貴方の運勢です。

『流年運』の運勢
　毎年巡ってくる、主星と従星がわかります。
　あなたの主星の巡ってくる順番はあなた自身のもので、宿命により決まります。
　毎年巡ってくる主星と従星により、どのような年になるかが決まります。
『月運』の運勢
　毎日巡ってくる、主星と従星がわかります。
　主星と従星により、どのような月になるかが決まります。
　従星の運気力で毎日のバイオリズムがわかります。
　従星のエネルギーの大きさを利用し積極的に行動することも成功につながります。

『今年』の運勢
　今年の運勢がわかります。
　また今年のあなたの主星と従星がわかります。
　巡ってきた主星に逆らわずに行動することが、良い結果を生みます。
　従星のエネルギーの大きさを利用し積極的に行動することも成功につながります。
　天凶節が巡ってきたときは、天凶節の意味を理解して慎重に行動することが必要です。

『毎日』の運勢
　今日の運勢がわかります。
　毎日巡ってくる主星と従星により、どのような日になるかがわかります
　また従星のエネルギーの大きさを利用し積極的に行動することも成功につながります。
　ただし、天凶節が巡ってきたときは、天凶節の意味を理解して慎重に行動することが必要です。

『天凶節』
　天凶節が後天運に巡ってきた期間は、その主星と宿命の主星の働きが弱くなります。従星の運気力は弱まります。
　引越、契約、転職、つまり新しいことを避けるように、または十分慎重に心がける時です。
　天凶節を明けたときのために、自分自身を磨く期間でもあります。
　後天運で吉星が巡ったときに、天凶節と重なった場合、吉星の福分は薄れます。忌星と重なった場合、凶分は薄れ、吉と転じます。
　ただし、天凶節の期間に慎重にに行動することにより福分を得る場合もあります。

『相性』
　自分に合う人、合わない人、人間社会でこの相性は重要なことです。
　友達、夫婦、上司、部下、親子、ビジネス。貴方の星はどの星と相性がいいのか悪いのかがわかります。

『女性のための相性』
　貴女と男性との相性を占います。

description:
EchoHacks Speech Trainer enables the user to speak into the microphone and
to hear back the user's own voice through headphones after a specific delay in seconds.
The voice is echoed back automatically, while standard audio recorders
would require multiple button clicks to duplicate this process.
(Bluetooth headset supported)

The tool has a wide range of applications and can be used effectively in training
for accent reduction, foreign language pronunciation, diction, articulation,
singing, public speaking, and interview practice.

Please visit the EchoHacks website to learn how to use the tool effectively
for your speech training.

EchoHacks Speech Trainer was created by the inventor who wanted to reduce his
foreign accent, and improve his public speaking skills. He developed the app
after realizing that no tools were available that would assist him to focus on
deliberate practice (focused high repetition drills) in speech training.

IMPORTANT:
* The app will only function with a phone headset.
* The app is a speech training tool and does not record audio.
* The app will run in the background.

*** TROUBLESHOOTING: Device is not recognizing the headset connection ***
There are some devices that do not auto-detect a headset connection, so the
the app won't run. In this case, you can use the SoundAbout app to overwrite
the default headset setting. Click on the Media Audio section and select Wired Headset.
In most cases, this will solve this issue.

If you encounter any problems, please leave a message on the website forums
(www.echohacks.com/forums) and we will do our very best to help you.

description:
Pedal Steel is a pedal steel fretboard analysis tool. First create custom copedents to match your pedal steel guitar. Then use the analysis tools and training tools to gain insight into the fretboard.

The Analysis tool allows you to select a key, fret and active changers. You can then view and hear all of the basic chord voicings for the selected key. The analysis diagram is interactive allowing you to turn changers on and off to quickly see the effect of each changer.

The Chord Finder tool allows you to select a key, a root note and a chord type and gives you a list of chord voicing options for how the chord can be played. Click a chord voicing option to view and hear the chord voicing.

The Copedent tool allows you to view a copedent diagram. You can also edit your changes directly from the diagram.

Images can be saved to the gallery for future reference.

The training tools include Copedent Basics, Identify Note, Identify Interval and Identify Audio Interval. These tools can help you learn your fretboard.

The training tools include options to let you target specific areas. You can exclude strings, frets and changers. For example, a beginner that wants to learn the open string notes would exclude all frets except 0 and exclude all changers. Once the beginner knows all of the open strings they can include some changers and learn which changers change which strings and by how much.

eMunity is a parent’s sure-shot solution never missing a shot. A perfect addition to every parent’s arsenal, this app makes managing baby’s immunisation, as easy as ABC.
The coming of a baby (or three) can be an overwhelming responsibility. Add to that the worries of remembering vaccines, understanding complicated and ever-changing immunization charts, grappling with jargon, keeping paediatrician’s appointments, and maintaining and carrying up-to-date medical records. Throw in sleep-deprived parents, guardians switching responsibilities and immunization norms that change by geography, and you have a recipe for stress.

eMunity is a handy helper that will help you effortlessly manage all your vaccination woes with a swipe or two. This smart immunization app frees you from charts and files and ensures that your baby keeps her or his date with the doctor. Because nowhere is it more true, prevention is better than cure.

Introduction:
When you download eMunity and add your baby’s details, it gives you a comprehensive list of all the vaccines that should be given as per your baby’s age. Once you’ve unchecked the ones your child has not received, you have a visual report of your child’s progress. You can now begin to use the app to easily manage your baby’s immunisation.

Features
• Add and manage details for multiple babies.
• Get a comprehensive and updated list of vaccines required for your baby as per age.
• Set reminders for vaccines that are due next, and even to manage your paediatrician’s appointments better.
• Share your child’s progress with a guardian, even in your absence. Share progress with family members.
• Get detailed information about vaccines and their effects.
• Demystify medical jargon. Get answers before you go for vaccination.
• Add custom vaccines in case of international travel.
• Store and retrieve your child’s medical records on your app.
• Access our continuously updated central repository for information on vaccines.
• Automatically receive timely alerts and information regarding vaccines.

description:
The National Council of Education and Research Training (NCERT) sets the curriculum and exam standards for schools following the Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE). NCERT solutions for Class 12 Chemistry is a free app solution that includes answers to problems given in textbooks and provides chapter-wise solutions for topics such as Electro-chemistry, Surface Chemistry, Coordination Compounds, and others. The Chemistry NCERT Solutions Class 12 provides step-by-step solutions to complex equations and tough questions which prepare students to crack the toughest papers without facing any difficulty.

NCERT Class 12 Chemistry Chapter-wise Notes :-

Chapter 1 - The Solid State
Chapter 2 - Solutions
Chapter 3 - Electrochemistry
Chapter 4 - Chemical Kinetics
Chapter 5 - Surface Chemistry
Chapter 6 - General Principles and Processes of Isolation of Elements
Chapter 7 - The p-Block Elements
Chapter 8 - The d and f Block Elements
Chapter 9 - Coordination Compounds
Chapter 10 - Haloalkanes and Haloarenes
Chapter 11 - Alcohols, Phenols and Ethers
Chapter 12 - Aldehydes, Ketones and Carboxylic Acids
Chapter 13 - Amines
Chapter 14 - Biomolecules
Chapter 15 - Polymers
Chapter 16 - Chemistry in Everyday life

Chemistry has revolutionised the world and changed lives for the better. From medical applications to gene studies, having a foundation knowledge of Chemistry better equips students to theorize concepts and bring applications to life. The CBSE Class 12 Chemistry NCERT Solutions have been written by some of the best educational experts in the country, thus making concepts easy to understand and grasp quickly. The Chemistry Class 12 NCERT solutions covers chapters and topics which appear in various entrance exams, like the JEE. Different types of questions that are asked in the textbooks can be repetitive or confusing, but NCERT Chemistry app solutions help deal with any problems while answering the questions or solving equations. Useful in individual and group studies, by practising these solutions, students can thoroughly prepare for academic exams and understand topics from a practical perspective. This acts as a gateway to the mind of the examiner.

Preparing for competitive exams, in addition to sitting for regular Class 12 board exams can take its toll on students, if not done with care. By studying solutions from these NCERT apps, students will have a better grasp of concepts and streamline their learning process.

- Adds a Validate option to the menu for checking to see if the entries made so far match the solution

With the DSB I-Signer app it is easier to log onto DSB Internet Banking and the DSB Mobile Banking app. You always have your DSB I-Signer app at your disposal on your smartphone or tablet. It is also possible to add multiple I-Signers to the DSB I-Signer app.

DSB Internet Banking enables you to conduct your financial transactions 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, in your own time, in your own way, with your bank, De Surinaamsche Bank. As you are banking online, you trust that your transactions are conducted correctly, quickly, privately, but most of all, safely. To ensure security and comply with the latest international standards, DSB has introduced: the I-Signer. The I-Signer ensures that in a world of rising criminality, you can safely continue performing your banking transactions with DSB.

Security
The I-Signer is an electronic device that helps you prevent unauthorized access by computer criminals, while you’re conducting your financial transactions via Internet Banking. With the I-Signer a “Two Factor Authentication” system is used, whereby besides the userid/password, the internet banking account holder requires a device to enable him to perform bank transactions through the net. The I-Signer has many advantages for its DSB
customers. For example:
• it greatly reduces the risk of security incidents in the internet banking environment.
• with the I-Signer DSB meets the international security requirements and standards for
financial institutions.
